Currently, sellers can create catalog publications with the content
(titles, photos, descriptions and data sheet) provided by Mercado Libre.
Listings can be made from current publications and thus compete with
other sellers having the best sales conditions to gain exposure on the
Product Page. These Pages are positioned in the first places of the
search results.

  

In addition, you can [see more information in the Seller Learning
Center](https://sellers.mercadolibre.com/news/catalog-is-here-a-new-way-to-sell-more/).

  

Now, develop catalog by following this guide!

eligibility](https://global-selling.mercadolibre.com/devsite/catalog-eligibility-gs).
